import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Paper, Box, AppBar, Toolbar, IconButton, Menu, MenuItem, CssBaseline, Button, Avatar } from '@mui/material';
import { createTheme, ThemeProvider } from '@mui/material/styles';
import { Menu as MenuIcon } from '@mui/icons-material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

const theme = createTheme({
  palette: {
    mode: 'dark',
    primary: {
      main: '#90caf9',
    },
    secondary: {
      main: '#f48fb1',
    },
    background: {
      default: '#1c1c1c',
      paper: '#2c2c2c',
    },
    text: {
      primary: '#ffffff',
    },
  },
});

function UserDashboard() {
  const [anchorEl, setAnchorEl] = React.useState(null);

  const handleMenuOpen = (event) => {
    setAnchorEl(event.currentTarget);
  };

  const handleMenuClose = () => {
    setAnchorEl(null);
  };

  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
      <CssBaseline />
      <AppBar position="static">
        <Toolbar>
          <IconButton edge="start" color="inherit" aria-label="menu" onClick={handleMenuOpen}>
            <MenuIcon />
          </IconButton>
          <Menu anchorEl={anchorEl} open={Boolean(anchorEl)} onClose={handleMenuClose}>
            <MenuItem component={Link} to="/showcase" onClick={handleMenuClose}>Showcase</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem component={Link} to="/pricing" onClick={handleMenuClose}>Pricing</MenuItem>
          </Menu>
          <Typography variant="h6" style={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            FlipVault
          </Typography>
          <Button color="inherit" component={Link} to="/login">Log in</Button>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Welcome Back
              </Typography>
              <Avatar alt="Tommy Style" src="/static/images/avatar/1.jpg" />
              <Typography variant="body1">
                Tommy Style
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Total Sales
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h4">
                $25,240.00
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Total Orders
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h4">
                3,469
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={3}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Product View
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h4">
                680K
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Balance Breakdown
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ height: 200 }}>
                {/* Add your chart component here */}
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Report
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ height: 200 }}>
                {/* Add your chart component here */}
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Recent Orders
              </Typography>
              <Box>
                {/* Add your recent orders component here */}
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 2, backgroundColor: 'background.paper' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Popular Products
              </Typography>
              <Box>
                {/* Add your popular products component here */}
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </ThemeProvider>
  );
}

export default UserDashboard;
